305
00:57:12,940 --> 00:57:15,620
- Will you have some watermelon?
- Uh-huh.

306
00:57:23,380 --> 00:57:25,460
- Hi.
- Hi.

307
00:57:26,340 --> 00:57:27,740
Look what I've got.

308
00:58:03,620 --> 00:58:05,020
What have you got on?

309
00:58:05,500 --> 00:58:06,660
