380
01:10:24,540 --> 01:10:26,340
- How much is here?
- I don't know.

381
01:10:26,460 --> 01:10:28,540
- Should I count it?
- There's no time.

382
01:10:29,540 --> 01:10:30,740
Quiet. Understand?

383
01:11:24,700 --> 01:11:26,180
You'll hitch a ride home.

384
01:11:29,420 --> 01:11:30,380
