Should we go back?

386
01:11:34,940 --> 01:11:37,660
Give me the money.
I need to take it right now.

387
01:11:45,220 --> 01:11:47,260
Hey, leave them. I love apples.

388
01:11:53,500 --> 01:11:54,740
Where's my share?

389
01:11:54,940 --> 01:11:55,740
